    "description": "<p>CHINA RAILWAY FIRST GROUP CO., LTD. SINGAPORE BRANCH</p>\r\n\r\n<p>China Railway First Group Co., Ltd. was established in 1950,with its registered office in Xi’an, shaanxi. As the backbone member of China Railway Group Limited, it is certified to possess Super Grade qualification for general contract railway, highway. During the past 65 years since its establishment, CRFG has built its landmark projects almost throughout the whole domestic China. And China Railway First Group Co., Ltd. Singapore Branch was established in 2016, and for developing our new MRT project: Singapore Thomson-East Cost Line T302 Project, we really hope you can join us!</p>\r\n",
